Usage: add_gui_marker [-help] -color <string> -name <string> -pt {x y}
                      -type {X TICK STAR}

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-color <string>         # The color of Marker (string, required)
-name <string>          # The name of Marker (string, required)
-pt {x y}               # The Location (point, required)
-type {X TICK STAR}     # (enum, required)